    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="close-modal" data-bs-dismiss="modal"><img src="assets/img/close-icon.svg" alt="Close product" /></div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row justify-content-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-8">
                        <div class="modal-body">
                            <!-- Product details-->
                            <h2 class="text-uppercase">Store Name</h2>
                            <p class="item-intro text-muted">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur.</p>
                            <img class="img-fluid d-block mx-auto" src="https://dummyimage.com/450x300/dee2e6/6c757d.jpg" alt="..." />

                            <p>Use this area to describe your Store. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Est blanditiis dolorem culpa incidunt minus dignissimos deserunt repellat aperiam quasi sunt officia expedita beatae cupiditate, maiores repudiandae, nostrum, reiciendis facere nemo!</p>
                            <ul class="list-inline">
                                <li>
                                    <strong>Address:</strong>
                                    Boolstr 122
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <strong>Shop time:</strong>
                                    5am-8pm
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <button class="btn btn-primary btn-xl text-uppercase">

                                Open Map for direction
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


